WINTER PARK TELEPHONE COMPANY, Appellant, v. SOUTHERN BELL TELEPHONE & TELEGRAPH COMPANY, Appellee. No. 13384. United States Court of Appeals Fifth Circuit. May 22, 1951. H. M. Voorhis, W. H. Poe, Orlando, Fla., for appellant. Robert J. Pleus, Orlando, Fla., for ap-pellee.

Before HOLMES, McCORD, and STRUM, Circuit Judges.

PER CURIAM.

The judgment appealed from is affirmed.
